can I see a different view.

296
00:15:03,656 --> 00:15:05,177
Yet all this is unknown.

297
00:15:06,536 --> 00:15:08,016
You're taking unknown risks

298
00:15:08,016 --> 00:15:09,297
for the unknown

299
00:15:09,297 --> 00:15:10,656
and paying unknown prices.

300
00:15:11,417 --> 00:15:12,577
Is that rational?

301
00:15:15,337 --> 00:15:16,136
Ms. Bai,

302
00:15:16,817 --> 00:15:17,776
a very important person

303
00:15:17,776 --> 00:15:18,817
once told me

304
00:15:19,417 --> 00:15:21,217
all the beauty in this world

305
00:15:21,937 --> 00:15:22,977
lies in the unknown.

306
00:15:24,776 --> 00:15:26,256
I'll take all my belongings.

307
00:15:26,496 --> 00:15:28,256
We should try to meet less from now on.

308
00:15:28,616 --> 00:15:29,776
It's for your own good.

309
00:15:30,376 --> 00:15:31,297
Ruoxi,

310
00:15:31,417 --> 00:15:32,656
what's really going on?

311
00:15:33,217 --> 00:15:35,136
You have to tell me what's happened.

312
00:15:36,057 --> 00:15:36,817
Previously,

313
00:15:36,817 --> 00:15:38,256
though you didn't let others know

314
00:15:38,256 --> 00:15:39,417
that we're sisters,

315
00:15:39,577 --> 00:15:40,577
I knew

316
00:15:40,697 --> 00:15:42,057
you were protecting me.

317
00:15:42,736 --> 00:15:43,457
But today,

318
00:15:43,457 --> 00:15:45,297
why are you taking everything away?

319
00:15:46,496 --> 00:15:48,057
Maybe I'm overthinking it,

320
00:15:49,057 --> 00:15:50,177
but remember this.

321
00:15:50,577 --> 00:15:51,736
If one day

322
00:15:51,736 --> 00:15:52,977
something happens to me,

323
00:15:53,457 --> 00:15:54,977
you only need to do one thing.

324
00:15:56,856 --> 00:15:57,817
Forget about me.

325
00:15:58,256 --> 00:15:59,616
Don't mention me to anyone.

326
00:15:59,616 --> 00:16:00,417
You hear me?

327
00:16:00,697 --> 00:16:01,616
No!

328
00:16:01,977 --> 00:16:03,937
Don't you dare say that! It's bad luck!

329
00:16:05,057 --> 00:16:05,977
Ruoxi,

330
00:16:06,217 --> 00:16:07,376
I'm grown up now.

331
00:16:07,656 --> 00:16:08,776
I can earn my own money.

332
00:16:08,776 --> 00:16:10,097
I don't need you to support me.

333
00:16:10,496 --> 00:16:11,896
Please don't leave.

334
00:16:11,977 --> 00:16:13,457
Stay here with me.

335
00:16:15,536 --> 00:16:16,457
Oh dear.

336
00:16:17,057 --> 00:16:17,616
I...

337
00:16:18,136 --> 00:16:19,577
I'm just kidding.

338
00:16:19,817 --> 00:16:21,417
I'm going to live in a villa.

339
00:16:21,656 --> 00:16:23,376
This place is all yours from now on.

340
00:16:23,376 --> 00:16:24,297
How great!

341
00:16:25,577 --> 00:16:26,217
Oh,

342
00:16:26,896 --> 00:16:28,337
I'm leaving this diary with you.

343
00:16:28,937 --> 00:16:30,016
I won't be taking it.

344
00:16:30,977 --> 00:16:32,896
It has a lot of my past written in it.

345
00:16:33,697 --> 00:16:35,337
I don't want Jiasheng

346
00:16:35,577 --> 00:16:36,297
to read it.

347
00:16:42,656 --> 00:16:43,417
Ruoxi,

348
00:16:43,697 --> 00:16:44,616
you know what?

349
00:16:45,177 --> 00:16:46,177
Leaving like this

350
00:16:46,177 --> 00:16:48,097
is choosing a whole new life.

351
00:16:49,217 --> 00:16:50,136
Although

352
00:16:50,656 --> 00:16:52,457
I don't know Deep In The Bustle

353
00:16:52,817 --> 00:16:54,337
or Tu Jiasheng,

354
00:16:55,177 --> 00:16:56,337
I do know

355
00:16:56,736 --> 00:16:57,896
that place is full of unknown

356
00:16:57,896 --> 00:16:59,136
and risks.

357
00:17:00,736 --> 00:17:01,697
But

358
00:17:02,177 --> 00:17:03,977
all the beauty in this world

359
00:17:04,256 --> 00:17:05,776
lies in the unknown.

360
00:17:12,137 --> 00:17:12,937
Ms. Bai?

361
00:17:14,576 --> 00:17:15,377
Ms. Bai?

362
00:17:17,377 --> 00:17:18,177
Su Yunian,

363
00:17:19,217 --> 00:17:20,256
please answer me.

364
00:17:21,417 --> 00:17:22,576
What's your relationship

365
00:17:23,016 --> 00:17:24,056
with An Ruoxi?

366
00:17:36,864 --> 00:17:40,538
♪If the heart can't hear the sorrow♪

367
00:17:40,837 --> 00:17:44,028
♪It only makes everything look so fake♪

368
00:17:45,632 --> 00:17:49,481
♪Your eyes resemble hers too much♪

369
00:17:50,030 --> 00:17:52,829
♪Who makes me forget whom♪

370
00:17:54,300 --> 00:17:58,030
♪The warmth in my heart is fading♪

371
00:17:58,254 --> 00:18:01,751
♪Every glance feels like atonement♪

372
00:18:03,150 --> 00:18:06,837
♪Ambiguity hidden in the night breeze♪

373
00:18:07,475 --> 00:18:12,590
♪Blows away the chance to explain♪

374
00:18:13,294 --> 00:18:17,428
♪I feel guilty♪

375
00:18:17,998 --> 00:18:21,742
♪I'll have no regrets
even I leave quietly♪

376
00:18:22,606 --> 00:18:26,049
♪Even in tears♪

377
00:18:26,798 --> 00:18:30,712
♪It doesn't matter♪

378
00:18:30,894 --> 00:18:34,717
♪We embrace in dreams♪

379
00:18:35,566 --> 00:18:39,004
♪I let down all my defenses♪

380
00:18:40,238 --> 00:18:43,601
♪Though the story has its end♪

381
00:18:44,366 --> 00:18:51,776
♪I'll journey with you all my life♪
